width of taking the lead against hosts France on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999570625980778, \"rank\": 4.293924441222106e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.894893112263536e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But mere moments later, Alexandre Lacazette drilled the ball into the back of the Americans' net \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and when Michael Olise added a second for the French side, they were on their way to a 3-0 win.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexandre Lacazette\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\"}, {\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Olise\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Olise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was unfortunate \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 on another day maybe it goes in,\\\" said Djordje Mihailovic, whose long-range effort came back off the bar when the Group A game in Marseille was still goalless in the second half.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Djordje_Mihailovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Djordje Mihailovic\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Djordje_Mihailovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Djordje_Mihailovic\"}, {\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.9702877337979171, \"rank\": 0.02390055171173926, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.20807141986431e-13, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_de_Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think most importantly, (we need to) emotionally recover because we were in the game for the first 70 minutes, even after they scored, we responded very well.\\\"\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the day, Morocco beat Argentina 2-1 in a game that was suspended for about two hours after fans invaded the pitch deep into stoppage time.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4765123125578197e-16, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA looked like they could produce another upset while repeatedly opening France up in the first Olympic game for American men since 2008.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999570625980778, \"rank\": 4.293924441222106e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.894893112263536e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999660194674148, \"rank\": 3.373990449758198e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not say anything to the players.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were in the right spot,\\\" USA coach Marko Mitrovic said.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have that feeling inside that we did not deserve to lose this way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA never came closer than Mihailovic's effort, and France made the most of their good fortune \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 responding with stunning strikes from Lacazette in the 61st minute and Olise in the 68th.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999570625980778, \"rank\": 4.293924441222106e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.894893112263536e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loic Bade added the third with a header in the 85th.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\", \"score\": 0.7570331434970577, \"rank\": 0.3209456747471748, \"text\": \"Bade\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bade_District\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew it was going to be tough.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You guys never give up,\\\" France coach Thierry Henry told American reporters afterward.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.894893112263536e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999660194674148, \"rank\": 3.373990449758198e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That fighting spirit is always in you.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You always believe that you can come back.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that.\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I played in MLS (Major League Soccer), I coached in MLS, so I know that's something that you have.\\\"\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"score\": 0.9999997723532746, \"rank\": 2.2764678243687456e-07, \"text\": \"MLS\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\"}, {\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"score\": 0.9999999998501607, \"rank\": 1.4993159302426992e-10, \"text\": \"Major League Soccer\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\"}, {\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"score\": 0.9999997723532746, \"rank\": 2.2764678243687456e-07, \"text\"